{"tid":878803,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"今日啲囡聽到我讀BLaw之後濕哂","createTime":"2018-10-27T12:04:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T14:50:09.000Z","uid":170668,"like":27,"dislike":205,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"91f8450c59301d14c4b9c04792b576e5b7144b5c","tid":878803,"uid":170668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T12:04:48.000Z","msg":"我就讀緊city BBA嘅，作為一個一大仔緊係要去二大HKU到食飯踩下場，於是就約咗個fd一齊食。<br />\n<br />\n頭先喺HKU canteen就發生咗以下片段<br />\n<br />\nFD：「你下個Sem Reg咗咩科呀？」<br />\n<br />\n唔知發生咩事成個人short咗，勁大聲咁回咗句：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「我讀Blaw啊！」<br />\n<br />\n瞬間HKU canteen入面啲囡知我讀Blaw全撚部望哂過嚟 搞到我都有啲唔好意思，有個重主動走過嚟搭枱　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ceedf84058471b81d2cca04122d4a507d4dd23","tid":878803,"uid":199310,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T12:06:18.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"190dbb2178a6d2be322c46ad6928a13e6952ec0f","tid":878803,"uid":215355,"like":9,"dislike":63,"score":-54,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T12:07:15.000Z","msg":"skr skr skr<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c0eba22e598913f58f133720ebf4c8576aefde1","tid":878803,"uid":164920,"like":44,"dislike":3,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T12:07:39.000Z","msg":"我BMedic tim la垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1552c7ac15acfab6a601d3ed8a8d21bfc6c44717","tid":878803,"uid":170668,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"190dbb2178a6d2be322c46ad6928a13e6952ec0f","tid":878803,"uid":215355,"like":9,"dislike":63,"score":-54,"citedBy":2,"replyTime